  "body": "Hey all,\r\n\r\nI'm aware that changing prune flags after sync is prohibited as outlined in #3658.\r\nHowever, I'm \"most\" (15m/19m) of the way through a sync of the BSC mainnet and have had a change of heart on not pruning.\r\n\r\nIs the general advise still to just resync, or is there documentation available on the tool referenced by [Alex](https://github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/issues/3658#issuecomment-1066014075)?\r\n",
